
#################################################
#                                               #
#                 Modules list                  #
#                                               #
#################################################
ChatServer.py	Code for server side
ChatClient.py	Code for client side
Consts.py 		Constants used in both server and
				client side.


#################################################
#                                               #
#    Note about terminating the ChatClient.py   #
#                                               #
#################################################

Due to the difficulty of handling ctrl-c signal 
with stdin.readline(), when want to stop the 
programs, please stop all the client first with 
CTRL-C and ENTER. Stop the server last with 
CTRL-C.